Text: (NYSE:SYY) Director John M. Cassaday sold 20,203 shares of the firm's stock in a transaction that occurred on Monday, September 16th. The stock was sold at an average price of $77.23, for a total transaction of $1,560,277.69. Following the sale, the director now owns 52,785 shares in the company, valued at approximately $4,076,585.55.
